NIMRO FIRE GIANT

Nimro Fire Giants are flame-touched supernatural giants with extraordinary
Physical Strength.  They are among the strongest of the OCC-eligible races,
rivaling some MDC beings in raw physical power.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 3-18   ME: 3-18   MA: 4-14   PS: 15-40 (Supernatural)
  PP: 3-18   PE: 12-32  PB: 2-12   Spd: 9-24

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 4d6 x10 (approx 40-240)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance (very high PS)
  - Giant size combat advantage
  - Fire resistance

PENALTIES:
  - Giant size limitations
  - D-Bee status in Coalition territory

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

